CUDA 11.2
PYTHON 3.10

2) GOTO: https://github.com/OpenTalker/SadTalker
Scroll down and DOWNLOAD:
Checkpoints - (C:\Users\YOURNAME\Documents\GitHub\FYP-25-S1-09\SadTalker\checkpoints)
